00:09:00,440 --> 00:09:05,320
Under oral performance conditions this feature enables the listeners to perceive the formal

114
00:09:05,320 --> 00:09:10,760
structure of the guzzle more quickly and we'll illustrate this when we look at an example

115
00:09:10,760 --> 00:09:11,760
later on.

116
00:09:11,760 --> 00:09:15,800
The last verse commonly includes the poet's chosen pen name.

117
00:09:15,800 --> 00:09:21,480
If it does this it's called a closing verse a monk the both these features reflect the

118
00:09:21,480 --> 00:09:25,600
