120
00:09:31,680 --> 00:09:32,680
Shared is poetry.

121
00:09:32,680 --> 00:09:34,040
Shyra is the poet.

122
00:09:34,040 --> 00:09:37,680
Mushyra is the performance of poetry.

123
00:09:37,680 --> 00:09:43,160
