126
00:09:51,720 --> 00:09:57,560
everybody's guzzles composed in this pattern were formally identical, sharing meter, rhyme

127
00:09:57,560 --> 00:09:59,000
and refrain.

128
00:09:59,000 --> 00:10:04,560
