134
00:10:25,480 --> 00:10:33,800
first line but not the second with possibilities for creating suspense, misdirection, surprise

135
00:10:33,800 --> 00:10:41,080
and so on that became major factors along with complex word play in the development of

136
00:10:41,080 --> 00:10:44,200
