162
00:12:47,600 --> 00:12:52,800
At the most basic level the guzzle is the first person voice of a passionate lover who

163
00:12:52,800 --> 00:12:56,280
laments his lack of access to his beloved.

164
00:12:56,280 --> 00:12:59,680
This lover is always construed as masculine.

165
00:12:59,680 --> 00:13:05,480
In some verses the beloved is very clearly feminine as for example when women's clothing,

166
00:13:05,480 --> 00:13:07,840
