167
00:13:07,840 --> 00:13:13,080
She is then either a courtesan or an inaccessible lady in Parda.

168
00:13:13,080 --> 00:13:18,720
In other verses the beloved is very clearly masculine as when the beginnings of the coquettish

169
00:13:18,720 --> 00:13:25,000
